Reports  <code>bind</code> used together with an arrow function.<br/>
Because arrow functions use lexical <code>this</code>,  a <code>bind</code> call will have no effect on them.<br/>
See <a href="https://developer.mozilla.org/en/docs/Web/JavaScript/Reference/Functions/Arrow_functions#Lexical_this">here</a> for details.
